q_A p_B + (q_A q_B) q_A p_B + (q_A q_B)^2 q_A p_B + \cdots  = \frac{q_A p_B}{1 - q_A q_B} = \frac{q_A p_B}{p_A + p_B - p_A p_B}.
\frac{\mu \delta + O(\delta^2)}{\lambda \delta + \mu \delta + O(\delta^2)} = \frac{\mu}{\lambda  + \mu} + O(\delta).
